&lt;p&gt;A station in Spain, Spain, December 2011, iPhone 4s&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Herbert Yang</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2013 20:00:00 -0800</pubDate><guid>tag:guizishanren.com,2013-11-28:vanishing-line/</guid><category></category></item><item><title>Photo#10 - East Lake 东湖</title><link>http://guizishanren.com/photo-series10-east-lake/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;East Lake is where my family usually went for sightseeing, picnic and hiking on weekends when I grew up in Wuhan, China. It's not as well-known as the world-famous "West Lake" in Hangzhou, China, but it's charming in its own right.&lt;/p&gt;
