Last Sloan Dinner on Thursday, June 13, 2013 at Vidalakis Dining Room in
Schwab. Great songs to close out our amazing rock band run in the Sloan
year!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe width="800" height="450" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/ZjHJnPgDKEA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Don't Stop Believin'&lt;/em&gt; (originally by Journey)&lt;/p&gt;
