hour to capture this memorable footage!&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Herbert Yang</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 03 Jan 2013 11:08:00 -0800</pubDate><guid>tag:guizishanren.com,2013-01-03:rock-band-debut/</guid><category>spillovers</category><category>coassf</category></item><item><title>Photo#01 - Dancers In the Park 公园中的舞者</title><link>http://guizishanren.com/dancers-in-the-park/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Zhongshan Park, Shanghai, China, iPhone4s&lt;/p&gt;
