&lt;p&gt;Youku: (China's version of YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNDYxNTUwOTA0.html"&gt;Click to watch the video&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
